</details>

🔧 **Installation**
<details open>
<summary>Show/Hide</summary>
<br>

Clone the repo to your local machine; navigate to project directory; install dependencies with "npm install" in the cmd line; Create a MySQL database and create the schema provided in 'schema.sql'; configure .env variables (use example as template); Run the application in cmd line "node index.js"; Follow the prompts to interact!

</details>

🚀 **Usage**
<details open>
<summary>Show/Hide</summary>
<br>

Perfect for keeping tabs on employees, departments and roles!

</details>

